MUSICAL
Section::::Musical .
In 2005 , comedian - musicians Jon and Al Kaplan , most famous for their musical re - imaginings of popular films as YouTube musicals , parodied The Silence of the Lambs , especially the film version , in Silence !
The Musical .
It premiered Off - Off - Broadway and has since had acclaimed productions in London ( 2009 ) and Los Angeles ( 2012 ) .
In 2012 , it won the Los Angeles Drama Critics Circle – Score , Lead Performance , Choreography Award .
